  "title": "Red star-like UFO spotted by ten people hovering over Brasília-DF [2002]",
  "URL": "http://brazilianufoarchives.com/2020/06/11/red-star-like-ufo-spotted-by-ten-people-hovering-over-brasilia-df-2002/",
  "short_URL": "https://wp.me/pc3ctW-k7",
  "content": "<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>JAN 24th, 2002</strong>. Time: 9:35 pm. Duration: &#8220;constant&#8221;. In Gama Sul, in the city of Brasília, Federal District, ten people spotted an unidentified flying object in the shape of a red star. The UFO remained stationary and had a &#8220;dot&#8221; aspect from a distance, but when it moved it made zigzag movements. The witness claimed to have recorded the sighting in photos, but these records were not made available with the present file. The report also informs that the conditions of visibility during the event were described as good and that there were no reports of condensation trails.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>Cf.</em> ARQUIVO NACIONAL (Brasil). Sistema de Informações do Arquivo Nacional (SIAN). Fundo &#8216;Objeto Voador Não Identificado (OVNI)&#8217;. Código de Referência BR DFANBSB ARX.0.0.620. &#8220;</span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">Questionário sobre avistamento de ovni no Gama Sul, Brasília, Distrito Federal&#8221;. Brasília, DF. 1952 a 2015. Último acesso realizado em 27/05/2020.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">The BRAZILIAN UFO ARCHIVES website is a private initiative and IS NOT endorsed or sponsored by the Arquivo Nacional do Brasil [see our &#8216;Info&#8217; page]. </span></em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>*THE ORIGINAL FILE WITH THE CASE REFERRED TO IN THIS TEXT CAN BE FOUND IN THE DOCUMENTAL COLLECTION OF “ARQUIVO NACIONAL DO BRASIL, LOCATED IN THE “OBJETO VOADOR NÃO IDENTIFICADO (OVNI)” FUND, UNDER THE REFERENCE CODE [&#8220;Código de Referência&#8221;] MENTIONED ABOVE.</em> <strong><a style=\"color:#808000;\" href=\"http://sian.an.gov.br/sianex/consulta/login.asp\">HERE IS THE LINK TO SEARCH THEIR WEBSITE</a></strong></span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"> </span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n",
